ul.li:
For Expression property, enter the following expression:${record:value('/pickup_latitude')}, ${record:value('/pickup_longitude')}

This returns the data from the two flattened fields in the following
                                format: <pickup latitude>, <pickup longitude>.

For the Expression property, enter the following
                            expression:
                            ${record:value('/total_amount') - record:value('/tip_amount')}
